OL,3,CBritish Airways to offer free in-
OL,4,Cflight access to messaging apps
OL,6,FBritish Airways passengers will be
OL,7,Fable to use messaging apps on flights
OL,8,Ffree of charge from next month.
OL,10,FThe airline said it will roll out the
OL,11,Fservice over two weeks from April 3,
OL,12,Fenabling travellers to send and
OL,13,Freceive text on apps such as WhatsApp,
OL,14,FiMessage, Facebook Messenger and Teams.
OL,16,FAll the carrier's Gatwick aircraft and
OL,17,Fmore than 80% of its Heathrow-based
OL,18,Ffleet have wifi, with the remainder
OL,19,Fexpected to be fitted with the
OL,20,Ftechnology by the end of 2025.
