OL,3,CBritish Airways to offer free in-
OL,4,Cflight access to messaging apps
OL,6,FPassengers must register with British
OL,7,FAirways' free loyalty scheme to use
OL,8,Fcomplimentary onboard messaging, which
OL,9,Fwill be restricted to a single device
OL,10,Fper person.
OL,12,FThose wanting to use apps to send or
OL,13,Freceive images, videos or attachments,
OL,14,Fbrowse the internet or stream content
OL,15,Fcan purchase passes costing between
OL,16,F#4.99 and #21.99.
OL,18,FEnhanced wifi access is part of
OL,19,FBritish Airways' #7 billion
OL,20,F"transformation plan".
