OL,6,FThis includes developing a new mobile
OL,7,Fapp and website, which will improve
OL,8,Fassistance given to customers whose
OL,9,Fflights are cancelled.
OL,11,FThe airline said the changes will
OL,12,Fenable passengers to book seats on
OL,13,Falternative flights, including those
OL,14,Foperated by other carriers.
OL,16,FPassengers entitled to hotel rooms and
OL,17,Ffood will also be sent vouchers direct
OL,18,Fto their electronic devices.
