OL,6,FTelevision presenter Steph McGovern
OL,7,Fhosted an event for the airline in the
OL,8,FCity of London on Monday night, at
OL,9,Fwhich she told bosses: "I'll be honest
OL,10,Fwith you, I hate the app."
OL,12,FChief commercial officer Colm Lacy
OL,13,Freplied: "I wish I had a pound every
OL,14,Ftime I heard that statement."
OL,16,FHe added: "Having a new technology
OL,17,Fplatform allows us to do things that
OL,18,Fwe just can't do on our existing
OL,19,Fplatform. It's all about
OL,20,Fpersonalisation."
